description:
High quality video and sound. Includes all music videos. A music video was made for every song on the Broken EP except for the song \&quot;Last\&quot;. This was traded in underground circles through record shops and NIN fans on VHS tapes. 

What I have here for download is the movie ready to watch on your computer or ipod. I have also included the entire album for your listening pleasure. Just paste the folder of music in your music folder on the c:/drive (hard drive) and Windows Media Player will read the info to bring up the album art.

The movie is about a killer who kidnaps a guy, takes him to his hideout and procedes to torture and kill him. The movie starts and ends with the killer being executed in prison for this crime. The movie includes music videos from Nine Inch Nails in between scenes to provide a unique look into the dark side of the human mind.

